00:37:29,550 --> 00:37:31,150
her life is going to change

867
00:37:31,150 --> 00:37:32,470
dramatically.

868
00:37:32,760 --> 00:37:33,360
It is quite normal

869
00:37:33,360 --> 00:37:34,760
for her to hesitate a bit.

870
00:37:35,000 --> 00:37:36,400
So you mean...

871
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:39,000
your mom will go?

872
00:37:39,510 --> 00:37:41,590
After all these years of training,

873
00:37:41,930 --> 00:37:43,680
my mom is no longer someone

874
00:37:43,710 --> 00:37:45,370
who doesn't know how to say no.

875
00:37:45,810 --> 00:37:46,960
The fact that she's hesitating

876
00:37:46,960 --> 00:37:48,030
shows that she still has feelings

877
00:37:48,030 --> 00:37:49,230
for Mr. Tang.

878
00:37:49,780 --> 00:37:50,580
It's just

879
00:37:50,610 --> 00:37:52,140
that she needs a little time

880
00:37:52,440 --> 00:37:53,970
to build up her confidence.

881
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:56,880
So,

882
00:37:57,760 --> 00:37:59,280
we just do nothing?

883
00:38:01,440 --> 00:38:02,630
That's not it.

884
00:38:03,590 --> 00:38:05,250
We still need to do something.

885
00:38:29,550 --> 00:38:30,080
Xiaolan.

886
00:38:30,150 --> 00:38:31,290
Mom, perfect timing.

887
00:38:31,290 --> 00:38:32,110
This is the suit Chen Xiliang

888
00:38:32,110 --> 00:38:33,520
tailor-made specifically for you.

889
00:38:33,520 --> 00:38:34,200
Go try it on

890
00:38:34,230 --> 00:38:35,230
and see if it fits.

891
00:38:35,590 --> 00:38:36,300
It's tailor-made?

892
00:38:36,300 --> 00:38:36,830
Go ahead.

893
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:38,130
This... This must be expensive.

894
00:38:38,130 --> 00:38:38,730
Not at all.

895
00:38:47,110 --> 00:38:47,670
Xiaolan.

896
00:38:48,440 --> 00:38:49,000
How is it?

897
00:38:49,280 --> 00:38:50,480
Do you think it looks good?

898
00:38:50,480 --> 00:38:51,360
It looks great.

899
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:52,900
Look in the mirror.

900
00:38:53,630 --> 00:38:55,430
Isn't this color too flashy?

901
00:38:55,590 --> 00:38:57,190
Not at all. It suits you well.

902
00:38:57,670 --> 00:38:59,150
You're a totally different person now

903
00:38:59,150 --> 00:39:00,670
compared to before.

904
00:39:01,550 --> 00:39:03,180
I don't think there's any gap

905
00:39:03,230 --> 00:39:04,630
between you and Mr. Tang.

906
00:39:04,920 --> 00:39:06,250
You have your own career

907
00:39:06,360 --> 00:39:07,490
and your own dreams.

908
00:39:07,920 --> 00:39:09,980
You are also so gentle and beautiful,

909
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:11,730
and you don't depend on anyone.

910
00:39:11,840 --> 00:39:12,840
Mr. Tang has never

911
00:39:12,840 --> 00:39:13,800
looked down on you.

912
00:39:13,800 --> 00:39:15,320
You should be more confident.

913
00:39:15,320 --> 00:39:17,550
Besides, look how beautiful you are now.

914
00:39:17,550 --> 00:39:18,360
I think

915
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:20,550
Mr. Tang is the one
getting the better end of the deal,

916
00:39:20,550 --> 00:39:21,150
isn't he?

917
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:24,920
Granny Yu.

918
00:39:25,230 --> 00:39:26,630
Xiaolan is right.

919
00:39:27,510 --> 00:39:29,770
You need to have confidence in yourself.

920
00:39:30,440 --> 00:39:31,710
Look at how well

921
00:39:31,710 --> 00:39:33,110
you're doing at your job.

922
00:39:33,230 --> 00:39:35,150
And you're so beautiful.

923
00:39:35,550 --> 00:39:37,000
Tang has good taste

924
00:39:37,190 --> 00:39:38,360
to have chosen you.

925
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:40,710
Don't sell yourself short.

926
00:39:43,550 --> 00:39:44,110
Here.

927
00:39:45,400 --> 00:39:46,280
Put this on.

928
00:39:47,280 --> 00:39:47,920
Granny Yu,

929
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:49,520
this is too precious.

930
00:39:50,760 --> 00:39:52,750
Fine feathers make fine birds.

931
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:53,880
Look.

932
00:39:54,720 --> 00:39:56,850
Paired with the outfit

933
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:58,140
Xiaolan chose for you,

934
00:39:58,150 --> 00:40:00,030
it's a perfect match.

935
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:01,590
Granny Yu,

936
00:40:02,320 --> 00:40:03,110
you've brought out

937
00:40:03,110 --> 00:40:04,130
your hidden treasure,

938
00:40:04,130 --> 00:40:04,940
right?

939
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:08,190
It's so beautiful. Thank you, Granny Yu.

940
00:40:08,190 --> 00:40:09,190
You're so biased.

941
00:40:11,000 --> 00:40:11,330
Look.

942
00:40:11,590 --> 00:40:13,790
Doesn't she look like the Mayor's wife?

943
00:40:13,840 --> 00:40:14,370
She does.

944
00:40:14,840 --> 00:40:15,360
Mom,

945
00:40:16,320 --> 00:40:17,780
have you made up your mind?

946
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:19,010
Are you going or not?

947
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:21,760
I'll go.

948
00:40:29,530 --> 00:40:30,280
Take it slow.

949
00:40:34,110 --> 00:40:34,840
Here you are.

950
00:40:36,590 --> 00:40:37,630
You have no idea

951
00:40:37,930 --> 00:40:38,850
how elegant

952
00:40:38,880 --> 00:40:40,840
my mom looked when she put on that suit

953
00:40:40,840 --> 00:40:42,110
designed by Chen Xiliang.

954
00:40:42,110 --> 00:40:43,360
Didn't you say before

955
00:40:43,540 --> 00:40:44,830
that Luna could start

956
00:40:44,850 --> 00:40:45,930
a high-end line

957
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:47,360
to make custom clothes for others?

958
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:49,320
In the future,
this will be called "Haute Couture."

959
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,400
I think nowadays,

960
00:40:50,660 --> 00:40:52,590
more and more people can afford it.

961
00:40:52,590 --> 00:40:53,650
We can make it work.

962
00:40:54,720 --> 00:40:56,120
Your business mind,

963
00:40:56,150 --> 00:40:57,400
full of intelligence, is

964
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:58,960
spinning so fast every day.

965
00:40:59,110 --> 00:40:59,630
Yeah.

966
00:41:00,190 --> 00:41:01,800
Someone told me,

967
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:03,630
"The sea's vast for fish to leap

968
00:41:03,630 --> 00:41:05,510
and the sky's wide for birds to fly."

969
00:41:05,510 --> 00:41:06,510
And since then,

970
00:41:06,510 --> 00:41:08,000
I've only been pondering over

971
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:09,670
how to make my career

972
00:41:09,670 --> 00:41:10,880
soar even higher.

973
00:41:11,110 --> 00:41:12,320
I will no longer think about those things

974
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:13,380
beyond my control.

975
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:14,400
Good.

976
00:41:15,230 --> 00:41:17,360
Then you just focus on flying.

977
00:41:17,730 --> 00:41:18,520
When you get tired,

978
00:41:18,520 --> 00:41:19,450
I'll go home

979
00:41:19,480 --> 00:41:21,880
and make you
noodles with fried bean sauce.

980
00:41:22,150 --> 00:41:22,840
Zhou Cheng,

981
00:41:23,560 --> 00:41:24,220
are you also

982
00:41:24,230 --> 00:41:25,280
a time traveler?

983
00:41:26,760 --> 00:41:27,820
Why do you say that?

984
00:41:28,000 --> 00:41:29,150
Because in the future,

985
00:41:29,150 --> 00:41:30,640
there will be a popular saying that goes,

986
00:41:30,640 --> 00:41:32,120
"Others only care

987
00:41:32,150 --> 00:41:33,230
how high you fly.

988
00:41:33,550 --> 00:41:34,230
Only I

989
00:41:34,440 --> 00:41:36,640
care if you are exhausted from flying."

990
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:39,220
It's still different.

991
00:41:40,320 --> 00:41:41,670
I not only care

992
00:41:41,840 --> 00:41:43,320
if you are exhausted from flying,

993
00:41:43,320 --> 00:41:44,720
but also how high you fly.

994
00:41:45,360 --> 00:41:47,690
You're trying to kill me
with the rat race?

995
00:41:47,800 --> 00:41:48,800
What does that mean?

996
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:49,550
Is this also

997
00:41:49,550 --> 00:41:51,350
a popular saying from your time?

998
00:41:51,670 --> 00:41:54,000
Then what will the world be like

999
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:55,400
in the future?

1000
00:41:56,360 --> 00:41:57,800
In the future...

1001
00:41:58,550 --> 00:41:59,280
Come with me.

1002
00:42:05,190 --> 00:42:07,320
In the future, this place will be filled

1003
00:42:07,320 --> 00:42:09,710
with plenty of towering buildings.

1004
00:42:10,550 --> 00:42:12,510
But even with all those buildings,

1005
00:42:12,880 --> 00:42:13,840
in every city,

1006
00:42:14,120 --> 00:42:15,070
there will still be many people

1007
00:42:15,070 --> 00:42:16,930
who can't find a home of their own.

1008
00:42:17,880 --> 00:42:18,320
Also,

1009
00:42:18,630 --> 00:42:19,430
in the future,

1010
00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:20,960
this pager

1011
00:42:21,280 --> 00:42:22,540
will soon be obsolete.

1012
00:42:22,620 --> 00:42:24,190
And cell phones will be eliminated, too.

1013
00:42:24,190 --> 00:42:25,920
Everyone will have a mobile phone

1014
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:27,030
and can afford one.

1015
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:30,000
It'll be very convenient
to contact people through mobile phones,

1016
00:42:30,000 --> 00:42:32,070
but you still won't be able to reach

1017
00:42:32,430 --> 00:42:34,030
the people you want to reach.

1018
00:42:34,880 --> 00:42:36,280
The speed of development in the future

1019
00:42:36,280 --> 00:42:37,920
will be very, very fast.

1020
00:42:38,510 --> 00:42:39,880
Everyone will be busy.

1021
00:42:40,170 --> 00:42:41,340
And more people

1022
00:42:41,360 --> 00:42:42,670
will leave their hometowns

1023
00:42:42,670 --> 00:42:43,870
and head to big cities

1024
00:42:43,920 --> 00:42:44,480
to fight

1025
00:42:44,510 --> 00:42:45,910
for a future of their own.

1026
00:42:48,630 --> 00:42:49,960
But that doesn't sound

1027
00:42:50,760 --> 00:42:51,280
much different

1028
00:42:51,280 --> 00:42:52,280
from the present.

1029
00:42:54,110 --> 00:42:55,670
How is there no difference?

1030
00:42:55,960 --> 00:42:58,000
By then, computers and cars

1031
00:42:58,030 --> 00:42:59,160
will be ubiquitous.

1032
00:42:59,400 --> 00:43:00,890
But in the end,

1033
00:43:01,080 --> 00:43:02,150
everyone will be tied down

1034
00:43:02,150 --> 00:43:03,880
by a tiny mobile phone.

1035
00:43:07,760 --> 00:43:08,760
What about the others?

1036
00:43:08,760 --> 00:43:10,160
I'm more concerned about

1037
00:43:10,590 --> 00:43:12,250
whether we'll know each other

1038
00:43:12,550 --> 00:43:14,030
and whether we'll be together

1039
00:43:14,030 --> 00:43:14,760
in the future.
